---
title: Stir-Fried Chinese Chilli Beef
description: Well, you could knock us down with a feather! When Patrick whipped up this little number, we were instantly transported to a bustling backstreet eatery in Hong Kong. It blew our socks off! The trick with this dish is to slice your steak into strips as thinly as you can. Next, you need to cook it in a super hot frying pan in batches. By leaving space between each strip in the pan, they’ll crisp up rather than stew. Let us know how it goes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/stir-fried-chinese-chilli-beef-wk5-1b749e4d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/stir-fried-chinese-chilli-beef-wk5-070dd883.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/stir-fried-chinese-chilli-beef-wk5-5847f64e4348d237547a1832
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Asian
nutrition:
  calories: 522 kcal
